]
}
]
},
"options": ["Hello", "World", "Welcome", "Hi", "end=\" \""],
"answer": [1, 3],
"explanation": "填空处应依次填入两个字符串参数“Hello”和“Welcome”。print函数会依次输出它们，默认以空格分隔。",
"example": "print(\"A\", \"B\") 输出：A B。同理，print(\"Hi\", \"There\") 输出：Hi There。"
},
{
"id": 5,
"type": "fill",
"title": "连词成句",
"content": "你发现下面这段代码能输出“我喜欢Python”，但有两个空需要你来填。",
"input": null,
"output": ["我喜欢Python"],
"code_segments": {
"segments": [
{
"type": "code_inline",
